Fran Mary Ryan (November 29, 1916 – January 15, 2000) was an American character actress featured in television and films. She was born in Los Angeles, California. ( not to_be_confused with Australian_actress_Madge_Ryan ) Fran_Mary_Ryan ( November_29_,_1916 – January_15_,_2000 ) was an_American_character_actress featured in television_and_films .
